{
  "name": "AllowEditRange",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong>AllowEditRanges</strong> 集合的 <strong>Add</strong> 方法或 <strong>Item</strong> 属性可返回 <strong>AllowEditRange</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p>返回 <strong>AllowEditRange</strong> 对象后，可使用 <strong>ChangePassword</strong> 方法更改密码以访问可在受保护的工作表上编辑的区域。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*在此示例中，ET 允许编辑活动工作表上的 A1:A4 范围，通知用户更改此指定区域的密码，然后通知用户更改成功。在运行此代码之前，工作表必须未受到保护。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>\n    sheet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Unprotect</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> wksPassword = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">InputBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Enter password for the worksheet&quot;</span>)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//Establish a range that can allow edits on the protected worksheet.</span>\n    sheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Protection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AllowEditRanges</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Classified&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>), wksPassword)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Cells A1 to A4 can be edited on the protected worksheet.&quot;</span>)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//Change the password.</span>\n    wksPassword = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">InputBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Enter the new password for the worksheet&quot;</span>)\n    sheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Protection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AllowEditRanges</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Classified&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChangePassword</span>(wksPassword)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;The password for these cells has been changed.&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上第一个可编辑的单元格区域删除。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Protection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AllowEditRanges</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表受保护的工作表上可进行编辑的单元格。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Range",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a>代表，它代表在受保护工作表上可编辑的区域的子集。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上第一个 AllowEditRange 对象的单元格数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Protection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AllowEditRanges</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Range</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例选中活动工作表上第二个 AllowEditRange 对象的单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Protection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AllowEditRanges</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Range</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Range",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Title",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置受保护的工作表上可编辑的单元格区域的标题。<strong>String</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将受保护的活动工作表上第二个可编辑的单元格区域的标题设置为“AllowEditRange2”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Protection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AllowEditRanges</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Title</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;AllowEditRange2&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示受保护的第一张工作表上第一个可编辑的单元格区域的标题。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Protection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AllowEditRanges</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Title</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "ChangePassword",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>更改受保护的工作表中可以进行编辑的区域的密码。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*在此示例中，ET 允许编辑活动工作表上的 A1:A4 范围，通知用户更改此指定区域的密码，然后通知用户更改成功。在运行此代码之前，工作表必须未受到保护。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>\n    sheet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Unprotect</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//Establish a range that can allow edits on the protected worksheet.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> strPassword = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">InputBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Please enter the password for the range&quot;</span>)\n    sheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Protection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AllowEditRanges</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Classified&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>), strPassword)\n\n    strPassword = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">InputBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Please enter the new password for the range&quot;</span>)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//Change the password.</span>\n    sheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Protection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AllowEditRanges</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Classified&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChangePassword</span>(strPassword)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;The password for these cells has been changed.&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上第一个可以进行编辑的区域的密码更改为“Y6dh!et5”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Protection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AllowEditRanges</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChangePassword</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Y6dh!et5&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Password",
          "type": "string",
          "description": "<p>新密码。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "Delete",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>删除对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上第一个 AllowEditRange 对象删除。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Protection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AllowEditRanges</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上第二个 AllowEditRange 对象删除。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Protection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AllowEditRanges</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "Unprotect",
      "summary": "<p>如果您忘记了密码，将不能取消可编辑的单元格区域的保护。建议将密码和对应文档名妥善保存。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>取消可编辑的单元格区域的保护。如果可编辑的单元格区域不是受保护的，则此方法不起作用。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例取消第一张工作表上第一个可编辑的单元格区域的保护。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Protection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AllowEditRanges</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Unprotect</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例取消活动工作表上第二个可编辑的单元格区域的保护。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Protection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AllowEditRanges</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Unprotect</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Y6dh!et5&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Password",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>一个字符串，它指定用于解除单元格区域保护的密码，此密码是区分大小写的。如果单元格区域不设密码保护，则忽略此参数。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        }
      ],
      "returns": "void"
    }
  ]
}